---
title: Roast Beef and Rosemary Roasties with Sticky Roots, Cavolo Nero and Onion Gravy
description: Nothing can bring people around the dinner table quite like the delicious smell of roast beef, fresh out of the oven. This British classic is perfect with the heart and wholesome flavours of root vegetables, cavolo nero and onion gravy.
